Today, a bit warmer for the feels like temperature (up 3.6°C) and outside temperature (up 2.7°C) and more moisture-laden outside humidity (up 8%) and rainfall (up 0.8 mm).

The past week and month had observable variation in light levels (up 9552 lux) and cloud levels (up 995 m) when compared to today.
